name: AXIAN DREAM WITCHTECH
description: 1st Edition #WitchTech #DeepWeb Single by BOSEBY, Art Work Directed by Lance MRSDN; Interactive Co. presents a cryptic #ambient sonic journey based on the original hip-hop performance Opt-Out From This World, self-published 11/21 by Boseby. Original source audio for sampling was derived from live modular synthesizer recording sessions spearheaded by the OG WaveMage. This is a liminal compression of what our moment in the foreground looks like to the outsider peering into our imbricated digital society.
